/// sometimes a valid handle value. See [here] for the full story. For APIs
/// like `CreateFileW` which report errors with `INVALID_HANDLE_VALUE` instead
/// of null, use [`HandleOrInvalid`] instead of `Option<OwnedHandle>`.
